definition: item/component/classifier for events, things, clothes etc

sentences.english: Customer can update the firmware expediently to acquire the latest function at any time.
sentences.chinese: 用户可以方便地进行固件更新，以随时获得最新功能。

sentences.english: Install the screws attaching the CHMSL to the liftgate.
sentences.chinese: 安装用以固定灯至车顶的紧固件。

sentences.english: The Fawer Fastener Subcompany is located in Jilin City, Jilin Province.
sentences.chinese: 富奥紧固件分公司位于吉林省吉林市。

sentences.english: Firmware upgradeable via USB on your PC.
sentences.chinese: 通过USB升级固件在电脑上。

sentences.english: The firmware also rectifies several minor issues to enhance operation.
sentences.chinese: 该固件亦纠正几个小问题，以加强合作。

sentences.english: Trust me, definitely SmartQ will fix the little issues in next firmware!
sentences.chinese: 相信我，智器肯定会在下一版固件中解决很多小问题。

sentences.english: Clip fastening part of headliner in rear area.
sentences.chinese: 卡入车顶衬里后面区域的紧固件。

sentences.english: New firmware for the DP1 adds composition grids for most shooting modes, too.
sentences.chinese: DP1的新固件在大多数拍摄模式中增加了栅格结构。

sentences.english: The appliance manager allows the firmware types to be deployed only to matching appliances.
sentences.chinese: 设备管理器只允许将固件类型部署在匹配的设备上。

sentences.english: Q7 - Can I install M33 firmware using this?
sentences.chinese: 我可以用这个安装M33固件吗？

sentences.english: With any other firmware, it will still be a brick.
sentences.chinese: 如何的之外的固件，那个也还用砖变得围起的事的呢。

sentences.english: Remove the kickstrip fasteners, the kickstrip, and the access plates for the floor attach bolts.
sentences.chinese: 拆下裙边紧固件，裙边，和地板连接螺杆的盖板。

sentences.english: P-TEC provides sleepers for various systems and rail fastenings.
sentences.chinese: TEC可以提供各种轨枕及轨道紧固件。

sentences.english: Scroll over the firmware to find printable words that can be significant.
sentences.chinese: 查看固件以找到可印刷的有意义的文字。

sentences.english: Global microcode compaction at present is an important issue in firmware engineering.
sentences.chinese: 微代码全局压缩是当前固件工程的一个重要课题。
